1. *Čuvaj* ključeve, da ih ne izgubiš. (Keep the keys, so you don't lose them.)
2. *Čuvar* je vrlo važan za sigurnost objekta. (The guard is very important for the security of the object.)
3. Moramo *čuvati* prirodu za buduće generacije. (We must preserve nature for future generations.)
4. *Čuvajte* se ulice preko puta, promet je jako gust. (Watch out for the street across, the traffic is very heavy.)
5. On *čuva* svoje tajne veoma dobro. (He keeps his secrets very well.)
6. Kako da *čuvam* ovu biljku? (How do I take care of this plant?)
7. Škola *čuva* decu dok roditelji nisu slobodni. (The school looks after the children when the parents are not available.)
8. *Čuvajmo* se od neznanja i lažnih informacija. (Let's protect ourselves from ignorance and false information.)
9. Ovaj pas je *čuvar* ovog imanja. (This dog is the guard of this estate.)
10. *Čuvali* smo mesto za vas. (We kept a place for you.)